originalText.text: You can be certain with these guys that making sure you find a place and are happy is the absolute lowest of their priorities. We applied through their broker Skye Foy, and they appeared great at first, we toured and applied for one of their apartments and were told we would hear back in around 2 days. They have since just strung us along for over 3 weeks and refuse to give us a response after taking a lot of our sensitive identity documents and financial information while they continue to show off the apartment. Extremely unprofessional and scummy company and broker.
